    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这个序章允许您使用《农场与超市模拟器》的有限版本进行生产和交易。通过将完整版游戏添加到您的愿望单来完成您的农场与超市模拟体验！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种植、收获、利用</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分利用您的收获产品：填满超市货架或将其作为动物饲料使用。选择权在您手中！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.poster.avif?t=1759788593\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.webm?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.mp4?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong>喂养与收集</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>喂养您的动物并收获奖励！喂鸡一个番茄，收集新鲜鸡蛋，享受劳动成果。[\\/p]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.poster.avif?t=1759788593\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.webm?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.mp4?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >投资机器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过购买机器扩展您的生产！处理收获的产品，制造超市所需的高价值商品。[\\/p]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.poster.avif?t=1759788593\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.webm?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.mp4?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收银员</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速扫描商品，接受现金或信用卡付款，确保顾客对购物体验感到满意！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.poster.avif?t=1759788593\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.webm?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.mp4?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>聪明工作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速将产品箱移至市场，填满货架，并满足客户需求!<strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.poster.avif?t=1759788593\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.webm?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.mp4?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超市扩展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用赚来的钱扩展您的超市！更多空间、更多商品和更多顾客意味着更多销售。战略性地组织您的货架，突出显示流行商品。[\\/p]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/9d36ee916c95c19b21644ae0de486d68.poster.avif?t=1759788593\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/9d36ee916c95c19b21644ae0de486d68.webm?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147710/extras/9d36ee916c95c19b21644ae0de486d68.mp4?t=1759788593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
